data.description: Beautiful well maintained home on a quiet street in Meridian's finest community, Tuscany!  Although this home is a 2-story, it seamlessly offers the convenience of single-level living. The master suite, a sanctuary of relaxation and luxury, is conveniently located on the main level, ensuring easy accessibility and privacy.  After entering the home, you will find a generously sized office or guest room next to a full bathroom.  Upstairs offers a bedroom, bathroom and bonus room.  Experience a harmonious blend of functionality and style with the open floor plan that promotes effortless flow and connectivity. The extensive hardwood floors throughout add warmth and timeless appeal to the interiors, creating a welcoming ambiance.  Step outside to discover a private, low-maintenance backyard retreat. Revel in the serene surroundings and appreciate the peace of having no backyard neighbors, offering a sense of seclusion and tranquility.  Built by Emmett Price, renowned as one of Idaho's premier custom builders.
